WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 37=

01:50.420 --> 01:51.260
Great Ancestor,

01:52.670 --> 01:53.580
are you alright?

01:58.470 --> 01:59.420
I know I was wrong.

01:59.420 --> 02:00.300
I was too careless.

02:01.190 --> 02:02.190
I fell for Yan Ke's

02:02.190 --> 02:03.220
diversion stratagem.

02:04.390 --> 02:05.230
From now on,

02:06.420 --> 02:08.070
stay by Duan Xu's side at all times.

02:08.700 --> 02:10.070
Don't let Yan Ke exploit a chance.

02:10.270 --> 02:11.110
Yes.

02:13.670 --> 02:14.510
But

02:15.740 --> 02:17.140
we can't track

02:17.140 --> 02:18.510
Yan Ke again.

02:21.550 --> 02:22.510
The elixir

02:23.420 --> 02:24.950
I gave Duan Xu just now

02:25.350 --> 02:26.390
can only temporarily ease

02:26.390 --> 02:27.460
his blood vomiting.

02:28.700 --> 02:29.540
But his five organs

02:32.230 --> 02:33.700
are damaged.

02:34.460 --> 02:35.830
I can't stop

02:38.350 --> 02:39.350
his body's decline.

02:52.267 --> 02:53.240
I'll return to the Void.

03:23.950 --> 03:24.790
The Spirits Lantern

03:24.790 --> 03:26.420
had become one with you.

03:28.620 --> 03:29.790
If you kill me now,

03:30.700 --> 03:32.110
you will only destroy

03:32.110 --> 03:33.230
the Spirits Lantern and me.

03:33.860 --> 03:35.180
Then your place as the Sovereign

03:35.510 --> 03:37.230
and the woman you can't have

03:37.790 --> 03:39.580
will be buried with me.

03:43.990 --> 03:45.620
I hold the Spirits Lantern's power.

03:46.230 --> 03:47.580
I can help you.

03:50.270 --> 03:51.230
Do I need help

03:51.230 --> 03:52.620
from a mere mortal?

03:53.830 --> 03:54.860
You can't control

03:54.860 --> 03:56.270
the power of the Spirits Lantern.

03:57.140 --> 03:58.510
I need not kill you.

03:58.950 --> 04:00.900
Sooner or later,
you'll face annihilation.

04:03.110 --> 04:04.620
The war is deadlocked for now.

04:05.510 --> 04:07.005
If you can't use the Spirits Lantern,

04:07.016 --> 04:07.990
you can't defeat He Simu.

04:09.350 --> 04:10.620
Teach me to use spirit power;

04:11.390 --> 04:12.860
I'll use the Spirits Lantern for you.

04:13.620 --> 04:14.990
We'll bring down He Simu

04:15.790 --> 04:17.180
and kill Duan Xu.

04:24.420 --> 04:25.910
I'll only teach you

04:26.670 --> 04:28.550
this cultivation method once.

04:29.500 --> 04:31.030
Memorize it.

04:44.500 --> 04:48.660
(Liang)

05:18.300 --> 05:19.140
At the time,

05:19.990 --> 05:21.940
the vanguard squad led by Chenying

05:23.790 --> 05:25.620
was split down the middle
by Chong forces.

05:27.860 --> 05:29.380
Chenying drew the enemy onto himself

05:30.940 --> 05:32.710
to buy time for the main force

05:32.710 --> 05:33.710
to meet the attack.

05:35.380 --> 05:36.620
But every man he took with him

05:39.150 --> 05:40.350
fell in battle,

05:43.500 --> 05:44.350
and not one returned.

05:48.350 --> 05:49.190
This is

05:49.380 --> 05:51.300
the Liang's banner
Chenying died to keep.

06:07.500 --> 06:08.940
This is all my fault.

06:11.350 --> 06:12.190
I should never

06:12.550 --> 06:14.060
have agreed to Chenying

06:14.230 --> 06:15.670
serving as the vanguard.

06:18.380 --> 06:19.940
I brought this upon Chenying.

06:42.180 --> 06:43.020
Xu.

06:45.670 --> 06:46.940
Xu, are you alright?

07:13.900 --> 07:15.740
(Zhaomu Pavilion)

07:15.740 --> 07:16.990
How are things in the Void now?

07:17.860 --> 07:20.180
Bai Sanxing led men through the Void

07:20.470 --> 07:21.213
and seized

07:21.224 --> 07:22.500
nearly all the puppet spirits.

07:23.670 --> 07:25.300
Bai Sanxing has been obedient lately.

07:26.956 --> 07:28.129
Thanks to you controlling him.

07:29.740 --> 07:31.740
He longs to tear Yan Ke apart.

07:32.060 --> 07:33.030
So, he spares no effort

07:33.030 --> 07:34.116
in catching puppet spirits.

07:36.836 --> 07:38.470
The Spirits Lantern
is still with Yan Ke.

07:39.550 --> 07:41.030
Luckily, he can't use it.

07:42.380 --> 07:43.380
There was an accident.

07:43.940 --> 07:44.820
He's found a way

07:44.820 --> 07:46.500
to use the Spirits Lantern indirectly.

07:47.470 --> 07:48.470
How could this happen?

07:49.536 --> 07:50.710
What do we do if this goes on?

07:51.550 --> 07:52.390
No need to worry.

07:53.550 --> 07:54.550
For Yan Ke to use

07:54.550 --> 07:55.470
the Spirits Lantern,

07:55.820 --> 07:57.300
it will still take some time.

07:58.233 --> 08:00.099
Send some Spirit Officials
to the Mortal World

08:00.110 --> 08:01.380
and report back.

08:02.790 --> 08:03.710
The Void's affairs

08:04.180 --> 08:05.020
are in your charge.

08:05.663 --> 08:06.689
I need to enter seclusion.

08:07.180 --> 08:08.020
Enter seclusion?

08:08.380 --> 08:09.550
Why at a time like this?

08:12.740 --> 08:13.740
Gather the medicines

08:14.470 --> 08:15.310
on this list.

08:15.310 --> 08:16.580
(Calculus Bovis, Borneol, Musk)

08:22.180 --> 08:23.030
How strange.

08:24.500 --> 08:25.820
I can't feel anything,

08:27.420 --> 08:28.420
yet in my chest,

08:30.230 --> 08:31.180
it seems to ache.

08:43.540 --> 08:51.100
(Liang)

09:02.110 --> 09:02.950
Xu.

09:03.900 --> 09:04.740
Xu.

09:07.470 --> 09:08.310
Xu.

09:09.420 --> 09:10.280
Xu.

09:10.420 --> 09:11.360
Xiaoxiao just taught me

09:11.360 --> 09:12.590
how to make a sugar figurine.

09:12.950 --> 09:13.900
Taste if it's sweet.

09:15.990 --> 09:16.930
Oh, right.

09:16.930 --> 09:18.590
I'll let Meng try some too.

09:22.990 --> 09:23.860
Han,

09:23.860 --> 09:25.260
I can never get this move right.

09:25.590 --> 09:26.590
Show me again, will you?

09:27.860 --> 09:28.900
It has to reach this spot.

09:29.660 --> 09:30.710
This strike needs force.

09:31.350 --> 09:32.190
Like this.

09:32.710 --> 09:33.550
Xu,

09:34.990 --> 09:35.860
Xiaoxiao is back.

09:36.350 --> 09:37.500
Let's get wine and meat pies.

09:37.830 --> 09:38.860
She loves meat pies.

09:39.199 --> 09:40.492
After she eats, she'll calm down.

09:40.590 --> 09:41.430
Come on.

09:47.110 --> 09:48.140
Come on, Xu.

10:43.950 --> 10:44.860
(Foxy,)

10:45.780 --> 10:47.260
(I won't let you die like this.)

10:59.740 --> 11:00.590
Your Majesty,

11:00.590 --> 11:01.663
Mr. Fang seeks an audience.

11:07.540 --> 11:09.350
Greetings, Your Majesty.

11:12.230 --> 11:14.350
Only Duan Xu didn't return to save me.

11:16.260 --> 11:18.020
By now, he should have arrived.

11:19.860 --> 11:21.140
Fang,

11:22.780 --> 11:24.380
why hasn't he returned?

11:26.710 --> 11:28.070
I know little of warfare.

11:28.380 --> 11:29.230
I don't know.

11:30.470 --> 11:31.780
Perhaps some mishap

11:31.780 --> 11:32.740
delayed him.

11:33.190 --> 11:35.620
Duan Shunxi is the Marshal
of the Three Armies,

11:36.380 --> 11:38.110
yet only he did not return.

11:43.860 --> 11:46.780
I know your talent.

11:48.310 --> 11:49.430
But, Fang,

11:50.660 --> 11:53.860
this world never lacks clever men.

11:54.860 --> 11:56.590
What it lacks is the right moment.

11:57.860 --> 11:59.430
You helped Jin save me.

11:59.900 --> 12:00.830
So,

12:01.260 --> 12:02.100
I shall grant you

12:02.430 --> 12:04.190
that moment.

12:05.350 --> 12:07.020
I will prepare an edict for you.

12:07.780 --> 12:09.230
You protected me,

12:09.900 --> 12:12.110
so you are titled Marquis of Zhonghe

12:12.740 --> 12:15.110
and promoted
to Vice Military Commissioner

12:15.830 --> 12:16.990
and Vice Chancellor.

12:18.310 --> 12:20.740
You can decide when this edict

12:21.950 --> 12:22.830
is revealed.

12:24.950 --> 12:25.900
Thank you, Your Majesty.

12:28.740 --> 12:29.710
Fang,

12:30.310 --> 12:31.500
do you truly want

12:31.500 --> 12:32.900
to live as Duan Xu's shadow?

12:37.660 --> 12:39.430
(Duan Xu led Great Liang's elite)

12:39.590 --> 12:40.620
(and marched to Youzhou.)

12:40.990 --> 12:42.780
(Liang)
(After months of hard battle,)

12:43.110 --> 12:43.990
(now,)

12:43.990 --> 12:45.710
(of the 17 Prefectures,)

12:45.900 --> 12:47.540
(11 are retaken.)

12:47.860 --> 12:50.660
(Only Youzhou, Fengzhou, Huanzhou,)

12:50.950 --> 12:53.950
(Jingzhou, Yizhou, and Guizhou)

12:54.140 --> 12:55.740
(Liang)
(are held by North Chong.)

12:55.990 --> 12:57.110
On the day I took command

12:57.110 --> 12:57.950
of the Three Armies,

12:58.950 --> 12:59.990
I made it clear to you.

13:01.020 --> 13:01.860
What we seek

13:02.780 --> 13:03.990
is to win battles,

13:06.110 --> 13:07.430
but to safeguard

13:07.430 --> 13:08.270
our people.

13:08.990 --> 13:10.380
The Chong cavalry is fierce.

13:11.590 --> 13:12.950
They once relied

13:13.310 --> 13:14.620
on their cavalry to sweep

13:14.620 --> 13:15.470
all the way south.

13:17.110 --> 13:18.660
They harmed our people,

13:20.350 --> 13:22.020
seized the 17 Prefectures,

13:22.590 --> 13:23.950
and slaughtered our kin.

13:24.860 --> 13:26.780
Now that we stand on this land,

13:28.550 --> 13:29.900
we must not take one step back.

13:30.430 --> 13:31.990
Our army stands here

13:32.100 --> 13:33.810
to defend our own land

13:35.430 --> 13:36.620
and honor the fallen souls.

13:49.740 --> 13:50.795
This is the Liang's banner

13:50.806 --> 13:52.780
Chenying died to keep.

13:54.140 --> 13:55.020
General,

13:55.020 --> 13:56.660
(Liang)
I want to fight on the field

13:56.660 --> 13:57.590
and defend our nation

13:57.590 --> 13:58.710
like you.

14:06.950 --> 14:07.990
Fight for our land!

14:08.230 --> 14:09.230
We must win!

14:10.190 --> 14:12.830
Fight for our land! We must win!

14:13.070 --> 14:15.710
Fight for our land! We must win!

14:15.950 --> 14:18.540
Fight for our land! We must win!

14:19.190 --> 14:22.020
Fight for our land! We must win!

14:35.260 --> 14:41.500
(Liang)

14:47.710 --> 14:49.310
Your Majesty, you cherish the people.

14:49.780 --> 14:50.710
You've raised

14:50.710 --> 14:51.900
pillars of the realm.

14:52.426 --> 14:53.609
Now, policies grace the court;

14:53.620 --> 14:54.753
the Chong forces are quelled.

14:55.310 --> 14:56.150
Prince Jin

14:56.310 --> 14:57.350
will surely not fail

14:57.350 --> 14:58.350
your hopes.

14:59.620 --> 15:01.430
Leave me alone for a while.

15:34.590 --> 15:35.660
Father,

15:37.950 --> 15:39.830
your most timid son

15:42.470 --> 15:43.860
has done all he could.

15:46.230 --> 15:47.310
In this lifetime,

15:50.230 --> 15:52.110
I could not live to see Great Liang

15:54.660 --> 15:56.260
reclaim all lost lands.

15:58.660 --> 15:59.830
I can only die

16:03.230 --> 16:04.070
with regret.

16:33.660 --> 16:35.990
(Three days
after the order returned to Nandu,)

16:36.189 --> 16:37.602
(the Emperor of Liang passed away.)

16:37.613 --> 16:39.076
(The New Emperor ascends the throne.)

16:40.070 --> 16:41.020
(At this time,)

16:41.020 --> 16:42.260
(on the north bank, Duan Xu)

16:42.430 --> 16:44.780
(led the Great Liang Army past Youzhou)

16:45.110 --> 16:46.260
(and smoothly retook)

16:46.660 --> 16:50.500
(Fengzhou, Huanzhou, Jingzhou,
Yizhou and Guizhou.)

16:52.020 --> 16:55.900
Long live Your Majesty.

17:15.060 --> 17:15.950
Young Master, bad news!

17:16.190 --> 17:17.030
Bad news!

17:17.910 --> 17:18.750
Young Master,

17:19.007 --> 17:20.147
thieves broke into the house.

17:20.923 --> 17:22.239
None of the valuables were taken,

17:22.390 --> 17:23.820
but the study was turned upside down.

17:34.310 --> 17:36.190
(The Analects)
I will prepare an edict for you.

17:37.500 --> 17:39.060
You protected me,

17:39.710 --> 17:41.990
so you are titled Marquis of Zhonghe

17:42.630 --> 17:44.710
and promoted
to Vice Military Commissioner

17:45.430 --> 17:46.710
and Vice Chancellor.

17:47.990 --> 17:50.430
You can decide when this edict

17:51.580 --> 17:52.580
is revealed.

17:56.863 --> 17:57.876
(The late emperor's edict)

17:59.780 --> 18:00.630
(is gone.)

18:02.230 --> 18:03.190
You've been

18:03.870 --> 18:05.340
the youngest Top Scholar of all

18:05.340 --> 18:06.820
since Great Liang was founded.

18:07.910 --> 18:10.630
Ever fearful, yet caring for the people,

18:11.500 --> 18:13.630
you bear the virtue of Yan Hui.

18:14.950 --> 18:15.790
Duan Xu

18:16.190 --> 18:17.630
has a noble family behind him

18:17.950 --> 18:19.340
and countless shadows.

18:20.340 --> 18:21.580
Your chance

18:22.500 --> 18:23.670
comes but this once.

18:25.340 --> 18:26.580
This decree of mine

18:26.990 --> 18:29.540
will raise you high
to fulfill your aims.

18:30.820 --> 18:33.430
After Jin ascends the throne,

18:34.230 --> 18:35.230
you will become

18:36.190 --> 18:37.670
his most capable minister.

18:41.260 --> 18:43.190
But to this decree,

18:43.740 --> 18:45.340
I must add one more clause:

18:46.580 --> 18:48.470
Duan Xu failed to arrive in time,

18:49.060 --> 18:50.910
harboring negligence
and treasonous intent.

18:51.870 --> 18:53.950
Upon his return to Nandu,

18:54.470 --> 18:55.990
he must be stripped of his command

18:57.230 --> 18:58.300
and executed.

18:59.910 --> 19:00.990
In all of Great Liang,

19:02.060 --> 19:03.060
he is

19:03.060 --> 19:04.390
the most exceptional general.

19:06.910 --> 19:08.020
But this blade

19:09.390 --> 19:11.230
must stay in my hand.

19:12.430 --> 19:13.270
From this day on,

19:14.500 --> 19:17.230
it must rest with the new emperor.

19:34.230 --> 19:35.070
Mr. Fang.

19:44.230 --> 19:45.070
Miss Duan.

19:46.540 --> 19:47.380
Mr. Fang,

19:51.150 --> 19:53.150
we made extra dumplings at home.

19:53.910 --> 19:56.870
Since you have no family in Nandu,

19:57.670 --> 19:58.510
I wanted

19:59.260 --> 20:01.260
to send some to your place.

20:04.430 --> 20:06.230
- Great.
- Good.

20:09.900 --> 20:17.580
(Yueran Fragrance)

20:23.340 --> 20:24.740
When unrest broke out in Nandu,

20:25.580 --> 20:27.740
I received an anonymous letter.

20:29.950 --> 20:31.580
Thanks to the warning in it,

20:32.740 --> 20:34.740
the Duan clan avoided the turmoil.

20:39.630 --> 20:40.870
Was that letter

20:43.340 --> 20:44.500
from you?

20:53.230 --> 20:54.070
I...

20:54.670 --> 20:56.020
I recognized your handwriting.

21:03.300 --> 21:04.430
So, Miss Duan,

21:05.710 --> 21:07.190
that's why you brought me dumplings.

21:15.870 --> 21:16.820
Actually,

21:17.540 --> 21:19.300
you and Xu must be

21:20.260 --> 21:21.100
quite close, right?

21:23.670 --> 21:25.260
In this world,

21:27.430 --> 21:28.740
others are the ones who owe Xu.

21:30.540 --> 21:31.950
He has never owed anyone.

21:39.100 --> 21:39.950
However,

21:42.500 --> 21:44.300
soon, he will owe me.

21:48.230 --> 21:49.740
Then I'll thank you for him,

21:50.500 --> 21:51.430
Fang Xianye.

21:55.710 --> 21:56.550
Xu.

21:56.870 --> 21:57.740
Xu.

22:05.950 --> 22:06.790
What is it?

22:07.470 --> 22:09.060
I can't tie this.

22:21.470 --> 22:22.390
In that case,

22:23.100 --> 22:24.740
could you call me brother?

22:29.990 --> 22:31.670
You have not joined my family.

22:32.430 --> 22:33.270
I...

22:33.990 --> 22:34.830
You are

22:35.190 --> 22:36.390
taking advantage of me.

22:37.730 --> 22:39.300
You are not my brother.

22:51.100 --> 22:51.940
Brother.

22:59.540 --> 23:00.910
Your essays

23:01.190 --> 23:03.580
are the finest in the realm.

23:04.390 --> 23:06.470
One day, you'll be the Top Scholar.

23:15.660 --> 23:19.940
(Duan Shunxi)

23:34.430 --> 23:37.710
Prince Ji and Prince Su

23:38.190 --> 23:39.300
raised troops for treason.

23:40.020 --> 23:41.500
Behind them stood

23:41.500 --> 23:42.430
Duke Pei

23:42.430 --> 23:44.300
and Chancellor Du.

23:45.340 --> 23:46.630
As officials of the court,

23:47.190 --> 23:48.430
they should serve the realm,

23:48.430 --> 23:49.710
yet they turned to treason.

23:50.740 --> 23:53.230
Bring up the guilty Yao Jianhe.

23:53.430 --> 23:54.910
The late emperor's edict is here.

24:03.950 --> 24:05.740
The late emperor's edict is here.

24:05.980 --> 24:08.580
(Decree)

24:08.580 --> 24:09.420
This edict represents

24:09.670 --> 24:10.710
the late emperor.

24:12.580 --> 24:14.260
(Decree to Fang Ji and Duan Xu)

24:23.390 --> 24:24.383
The late emperor's edict:

24:25.000 --> 24:26.786
Fang Ji earned merit
protecting the Emperor.

24:27.096 --> 24:29.429
He is made Vice Military Commissioner
and Vice Chancellor.

24:29.630 --> 24:31.430
Duan Xu failed
in protecting the Emperor.

24:31.526 --> 24:32.712
He harbored treasonous intent.

24:33.150 --> 24:34.100
He must be put to death.

24:34.500 --> 24:36.780
It bears the late emperor's seal.

24:36.950 --> 24:37.820
It's absolutely true.

24:38.430 --> 24:39.300
How dare you!

24:39.740 --> 24:41.670
Marshal Duan commands the Three Armies.

24:41.990 --> 24:43.630
He is still fighting
for us at the front.

24:43.930 --> 24:44.780
Your Majesty,

24:44.780 --> 24:46.100
you should execute

24:46.230 --> 24:47.580
such a treasonous rebel

24:47.820 --> 24:48.660
at once.

24:48.820 --> 24:49.660
How dare you!

24:49.830 --> 24:51.163
This is the late emperor's edict.

24:51.260 --> 24:52.100
Do you want

24:52.300 --> 24:53.710
to defy the imperial edict?

25:06.430 --> 25:07.270
Xianye,

25:08.100 --> 25:09.060
if you had such an edict

25:09.780 --> 25:12.300
to aid the rightful ruler
and strike rebels,

25:12.670 --> 25:14.630
why not present it
to His Majesty sooner?

25:14.990 --> 25:17.150
This was your perfect chance

25:17.150 --> 25:17.990
to rise to power.

25:17.990 --> 25:18.830
Mentor,

25:19.870 --> 25:21.150
why are you doing this to me?

25:29.100 --> 25:29.990
Your Majesty,

25:30.540 --> 25:31.780
I'd like to report a matter.

25:32.500 --> 25:33.740
Please punish me.

25:36.540 --> 25:37.390
Yao Jianhe ordered me

25:38.060 --> 25:39.100
to forge

25:39.100 --> 25:40.390
this edict.

25:40.670 --> 25:41.510
Fang Xianye!

25:43.820 --> 25:45.340
Yao Jianhe was my honored teacher.

25:45.820 --> 25:47.390
I could not bear to see him suffer,

25:47.670 --> 25:49.340
so I had no choice but to obey.

25:49.710 --> 25:50.820
What utter nonsense.

25:51.020 --> 25:51.860
Fang Xianye!

25:51.990 --> 25:53.020
You...

25:53.630 --> 25:55.340
You held the late emperor's edict

25:55.446 --> 25:56.540
yet refused to hand it over,

25:56.670 --> 25:59.230
joining Duan Xu in defying
the imperial edict.

25:59.950 --> 26:00.790
I am guilty.

26:01.390 --> 26:03.300
I shouldn't have followed

26:03.539 --> 26:04.625
vile courtiers into treason

26:04.870 --> 26:06.630
just because of the mentorial bond.

26:38.580 --> 26:40.100
Since the late emperor passed away,

26:41.430 --> 26:43.020
he has visited my dreams nightly,

26:43.580 --> 26:45.950
fiercely rebuking me
for framing loyal officials.

26:46.870 --> 26:48.060
I was consumed by dread

26:48.230 --> 26:49.870
and resolved to destroy
the forged edict,

26:50.150 --> 26:51.820
yet it was stolen by the rebel faction.

26:56.260 --> 26:57.100
Your Majesty,

26:57.230 --> 26:58.670
I dare not deceive you.

26:59.300 --> 27:00.670
Nor can I face my honored teacher.

27:01.100 --> 27:01.950
Your Majesty,

27:02.230 --> 27:03.350
please purge the conspirators

27:03.580 --> 27:05.100
and restore the order of the court.

27:06.100 --> 27:06.990
You insolent fool!

27:07.500 --> 27:08.740
You insolent fool!

27:09.020 --> 27:09.910
Fang Xianye!

27:10.100 --> 27:11.820
Have you lost your mind?

27:24.500 --> 27:26.870
I have committed high treason

27:27.870 --> 27:29.630
by trying to ruin a loyal subject.

27:30.910 --> 27:32.300
My crime is beyond pardon.

27:36.470 --> 27:38.100
Before the late emperor's spirit,

27:39.540 --> 27:41.020
I am too ashamed.

27:41.950 --> 27:43.710
Only death remains for me.

27:44.670 --> 27:45.510
Fang Ji!

27:53.540 --> 27:54.470
This...

28:01.020 --> 28:01.860
Xianye!

28:07.150 --> 28:08.780
(If I make this edict a forged one,)

28:09.740 --> 28:10.950
(Duan Xu may be spared.)

28:15.100 --> 28:15.940
(If I die,)

28:16.670 --> 28:17.990
(there will be no witnesses left.)

28:20.710 --> 28:21.550
(Duan Shunxi,)

28:23.300 --> 28:24.780
(you still owe me in the end.)

28:28.910 --> 28:30.430
Drag this rebel out

28:30.780 --> 28:32.780
for the ultimate punishment.

28:32.780 --> 28:33.620
Yes.

28:53.230 --> 28:54.070
Put it here.

28:54.950 --> 28:55.790
Careful.

28:56.160 --> 28:57.020
These are

28:57.020 --> 28:57.990
Xu's favorite books.

28:58.300 --> 28:59.340
Don't damage any of them.

28:59.670 --> 29:00.510
Yes.

29:04.110 --> 29:04.950
Jingyuan.

29:04.950 --> 29:05.790
Come in.

29:07.580 --> 29:08.540
Keep tidying up.

29:08.540 --> 29:09.380
All right.

29:14.820 --> 29:15.660
Father,

29:15.990 --> 29:17.230
what did you want with me?

29:19.580 --> 29:20.870
What has pleased you so today?

29:22.020 --> 29:23.780
Nandu has been stable lately.

29:23.780 --> 29:25.060
Xu fought at the frontier.

29:25.500 --> 29:27.780
He'll return
with illustrious military merit.

29:28.300 --> 29:30.190
Now, even his greatest rival,

29:30.540 --> 29:31.870
Fang Xianye, is dead.

29:32.740 --> 29:34.390
Someone who should've died long ago

29:34.670 --> 29:36.820
somehow clung to life till now.

29:38.630 --> 29:40.500
My wish is fulfilled.

29:41.230 --> 29:42.710
Now, it is time to settle your future.

29:43.470 --> 29:44.310
Come.

29:44.630 --> 29:45.470
On this list

29:46.150 --> 29:47.910
are eligible noble scions of Nandu,

29:48.670 --> 29:49.850
such as the Grand Master's son

29:50.300 --> 29:52.500
and the Duke of Lu's son.

29:53.230 --> 29:54.470
Though I have retired,

29:55.060 --> 29:57.060
with your Xu in Nandu,

29:57.430 --> 29:59.300
the Duan clan
is still of illustrious standing.

30:00.020 --> 30:01.260
You are my legitimate daughter.

30:02.206 --> 30:03.500
You must marry into a great house

30:03.511 --> 30:04.921
to carry on the Duan clan's honor.

30:05.780 --> 30:07.340
Look over these young men first.

30:07.710 --> 30:08.550
If one suits you,

30:08.710 --> 30:10.470
I'll arrange a marriage proposal.

30:21.060 --> 30:21.900
I don't like them.

30:22.630 --> 30:23.780
You have not even looked yet.

30:23.780 --> 30:24.870
How can you dislike them?

30:26.190 --> 30:27.030
I said it already.

30:27.950 --> 30:28.790
I don't like them.

30:29.870 --> 30:31.060
Was taking over Xu's life

30:31.060 --> 30:31.900
not enough for you?

30:32.530 --> 30:33.618
Now, you want to take over

30:33.629 --> 30:34.396
my life as well?

30:38.580 --> 30:39.420
You...

30:47.780 --> 30:49.240
Suddenly, I miss my younger sister.

30:50.230 --> 30:51.323
You are very much like her.

30:55.630 --> 30:56.470
Me?

31:00.740 --> 31:04.360
♪In silence, I gaze at you♪

31:04.560 --> 31:08.290
♪My hand hangs and then falls♪

31:08.640 --> 31:12.200
♪Let what stays unsaid pass♪

31:13.040 --> 31:16.450
♪Why torture each other like this?♪

31:16.730 --> 31:20.000
♪My wish might be♪

31:20.220 --> 31:23.600
♪Scattering like ripples♪

31:23.910 --> 31:29.990
♪With a gust of wind,
they fade like a dream♪

31:31.760 --> 31:35.620
♪Daylight fades into ash♪

31:35.620 --> 31:39.580
(Yueran Fragrance)

31:39.600 --> 31:42.920
♪For the rest of my life♪

31:43.870 --> 31:44.710
Jingyuan.

31:46.470 --> 31:47.630
May you find a worthy husband,

31:49.150 --> 31:50.430
be blessed with many children,

31:53.100 --> 31:54.060
and live a happy life.

31:54.570 --> 31:59.640
♪Collapse piece by piece♪

31:59.740 --> 32:00.580
Promise me,

32:03.260 --> 32:04.100
all right?

32:06.740 --> 32:10.290
♪And did not dare draw near again♪

32:10.440 --> 32:13.230
♪Leaving all behind♪

32:13.530 --> 32:18.000
♪The sudden pause of words unsaid♪

32:18.350 --> 32:21.760
♪How I long
to hold that silhouette close♪

32:22.170 --> 32:25.680
♪After waking up, we walk back-to-back♪

32:27.580 --> 32:28.420
Milady,

32:29.230 --> 32:30.300
why are you crying?

32:31.340 --> 32:32.860
(Yueran Fragrance)

32:33.730 --> 32:37.720
♪How I long
to hold that silhouette close♪

32:37.860 --> 32:41.320
♪After waking up, we walk back-to-back♪

32:41.440 --> 32:45.250
♪Watching all that is unfinished♪

32:45.430 --> 32:50.480
♪Fade away♪

32:57.820 --> 32:58.660
I have met him

32:59.710 --> 33:01.710
fewer than five times.

33:04.300 --> 33:05.150
Why?

33:05.150 --> 33:08.360
♪In the end,
love is the hardest to resist♪

33:09.020 --> 33:11.540
Why does he grieve me so deeply?

33:12.560 --> 33:15.290
♪Alone, I gather them up♪

33:15.480 --> 33:19.730
♪Like petals in the spring sun♪

33:20.270 --> 33:23.750
♪Till the past falls still again♪

33:25.100 --> 33:27.950
(Yueran Fragrance)

33:27.950 --> 33:36.580
♪The wind returns with my dreams♪

33:36.580 --> 33:39.420
(Liang)

34:17.220 --> 34:18.060
Unexpectedly,

34:18.540 --> 34:19.990
our long-held wish is near.

34:21.870 --> 34:23.540
So many years have passed.

34:25.020 --> 34:26.540
Back then, I drew you into this cause,

34:27.470 --> 34:28.310
yet in the end,

34:28.700 --> 34:29.580
I asked you instead,

34:30.910 --> 34:31.750
"In this world,"

34:32.990 --> 34:34.323
"can things truly go as we hoped?"

34:39.470 --> 34:40.310
You said,

34:41.620 --> 34:42.580
"It doesn't matter."

34:44.100 --> 34:45.140
"We need only try first."

34:46.390 --> 34:47.230
"The deepest night"

34:47.700 --> 34:48.540
"heralds the dawn."

34:50.830 --> 34:51.830
It feels like yesterday.

34:54.220 --> 34:55.060
Xianye.

34:57.950 --> 34:59.020
I spent a lifetime alone.

34:59.756 --> 35:00.742
I lost my parents young.

35:01.180 --> 35:02.270
I had only one confidant

35:02.660 --> 35:03.999
and a girl that I loved for years

35:04.390 --> 35:05.990
and never let her know.

35:11.060 --> 35:12.310
I'll leave the future dawn

35:13.270 --> 35:14.660
for you to see.

35:17.660 --> 35:18.500
I shall

35:19.060 --> 35:19.900
leave first.

35:35.220 --> 35:36.060
Fang Ji.

35:41.020 --> 35:41.860
Fang Ji.

35:42.790 --> 35:43.630
Fang Ji!

35:55.270 --> 35:56.790
Marshal, urgent word from Nandu.

36:00.950 --> 36:01.910
Marshal,

36:01.910 --> 36:02.750
a message from Nandu.

36:03.270 --> 36:04.536
Prince Jin has taken the throne.

36:09.750 --> 36:10.660
Mr. Fang is dead.

36:28.860 --> 36:32.340
(The forerunner met his end
in the wild.)

36:35.830 --> 36:36.910
Chaos broke out in Nandu.

36:37.270 --> 36:38.580
Prince Su and Prince Ji rebelled.

36:39.060 --> 36:40.580
The late emperor called for aid.

36:40.790 --> 36:41.700
But the court messenger

36:41.700 --> 36:42.750
never reached here.

36:43.470 --> 36:44.700
Now, His Majesty has learned

36:45.060 --> 36:46.220
that the Pei faction

36:46.430 --> 36:47.540
framed you on purpose.

36:47.860 --> 36:48.820
(To Shunxi, From Xianye)

36:48.870 --> 36:50.350
Fang Xianye, Vice Minister of Revenue,

36:50.830 --> 36:52.390
drafted a fake edict to accuse you.

36:53.470 --> 36:54.500
After it was exposed,

36:55.923 --> 36:57.149
he died by striking a pillar.

37:04.540 --> 37:05.380
(Shunxi,)

37:06.910 --> 37:07.910
(Nandu is now at peace.)

37:08.540 --> 37:09.500
(No need to worry.)

37:11.060 --> 37:12.990
(I have not seen you in many years.)

37:13.910 --> 37:14.990
(How brief a life is.)

37:15.317 --> 37:16.417
(We've parted for so long.)

37:17.950 --> 37:19.396
(Our paths differ with the same aim.)

37:20.430 --> 37:21.500
(Now, my task is done.)

37:22.270 --> 37:23.430
(Death is enough for me.)

37:24.613 --> 37:25.626
(It concerns no one else.)

37:26.290 --> 37:27.576
(Life is full of uncertainties.)

37:29.060 --> 37:30.540
(When you reclaim the land,)

37:31.700 --> 37:33.270
(please pour wine to tell me.)

37:41.580 --> 37:42.420
Marshal.

37:44.350 --> 37:45.190
Marshal!

37:46.580 --> 37:47.420
Marshal.

37:49.180 --> 37:50.020
Physician!

37:50.470 --> 37:51.830
(I lived a lonely life.)

37:52.870 --> 37:53.710
(You are)

37:54.220 --> 37:55.060
(my only kin,)

37:55.830 --> 37:56.670
(my dearest friend,)

37:57.700 --> 37:59.180
(and my true confidant.)

38:00.220 --> 38:01.990
(From: Xianye)

38:14.020 --> 38:15.220
This time, I can do no more.

38:16.270 --> 38:17.790
I've sent word to Great Ancestor.

38:18.350 --> 38:19.220
I only hope she can

38:20.060 --> 38:21.430
bring the medicine back asap.

38:23.620 --> 38:24.460
Great Ancestor.

39:26.910 --> 39:27.910
You nearly died.

39:31.350 --> 39:32.190
Simu.

39:35.100 --> 39:35.940
Simu,

39:38.060 --> 39:39.020
Fang Xianye...

39:40.500 --> 39:41.700
Fang Xianye took his own life.

39:43.580 --> 39:44.470
Take me to him.

39:46.060 --> 39:47.100
I need to see him.

40:17.060 --> 40:17.950
Duan Shunxi.

40:28.950 --> 40:30.950
When I was taken to North Chong,

40:35.310 --> 40:37.430
my father forced Fang Xianye back

40:40.870 --> 40:41.910
to stand in for me.

40:43.350 --> 40:44.350
After I returned,

40:47.100 --> 40:48.910
my father nearly silenced him.

40:50.790 --> 40:52.910
He had every reason
to hate the Duan clan,

40:54.310 --> 40:55.270
but he never once

40:55.270 --> 40:56.110
mentioned it to me.

40:57.180 --> 40:58.700
If we had not shared the same cause,

41:00.830 --> 41:02.060
Fang Xianye and I

41:05.060 --> 41:06.620
should have been enemies.

41:10.660 --> 41:11.830
I had always thought

41:14.270 --> 41:15.790
that once the war was over,

41:18.100 --> 41:19.270
I would place everything

41:19.270 --> 41:20.220
in his hands.

41:23.430 --> 41:24.700
Yet he left before I could.

41:26.660 --> 41:27.620
Now that I think on it,

41:29.470 --> 41:30.430
how can I be sure

41:30.430 --> 41:31.500
that what I set out to do

41:33.660 --> 41:35.140
will never come to nothing?

41:39.310 --> 41:40.390
Flesh and blood

41:43.660 --> 41:45.020
can't withstand fate's turns.

41:53.310 --> 41:54.180
Duan Shunxi,

41:57.950 --> 41:59.700
your light will also fade one day.

42:00.990 --> 42:01.990
Fang Xianye

42:01.990 --> 42:03.100
only went before you.

42:07.140 --> 42:08.430
You're just a mortal.

42:10.870 --> 42:11.750
Look at me.

42:13.020 --> 42:14.390
I haven't learned to accept parting

42:14.390 --> 42:15.310
for 400 years.

42:21.470 --> 42:23.140
Fang Xianye died with no regrets

42:24.310 --> 42:25.310
but a clear conscience.

42:26.620 --> 42:27.540
He would not blame you.

42:29.390 --> 42:30.870
He'd be glad that he met you,

42:31.910 --> 42:33.430
so he could become himself again.

42:35.350 --> 42:36.660
Just remember him.

42:53.750 --> 42:54.590
(Fang Ji,)

42:56.580 --> 42:57.889
(in your next life, don't meet)

42:57.900 --> 42:59.140
(someone as troublesome as me.)

43:01.020 --> 43:01.950
(Live more lightly,)

43:04.270 --> 43:05.350
(and go find your own joy.)

43:13.200 --> 43:18.530
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

43:18.860 --> 43:23.110
♪Light encountered shadow♪

43:24.470 --> 43:29.840
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

43:30.140 --> 43:34.740
♪The unbreakable fate♪

43:35.830 --> 43:37.670
♪Suddenly cracked♪

43:49.880 --> 43:55.320
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

43:55.500 --> 43:59.830
♪Light encountered shadow♪

44:01.200 --> 44:06.590
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

44:06.820 --> 44:10.760
♪The unbreakable fate♪

44:12.530 --> 44:14.420
♪Suddenly cracked♪

44:17.080 --> 44:20.240
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

44:20.240 --> 44:22.770
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

44:22.770 --> 44:28.290
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

44:28.290 --> 44:31.530
♪Following fate's guidance♪

44:31.530 --> 44:36.390
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

44:36.730 --> 44:39.750
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

44:39.750 --> 44:42.570
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

44:42.830 --> 44:45.360
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

44:45.360 --> 44:50.780
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

44:50.950 --> 44:54.020
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

44:54.180 --> 44:59.080
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

44:59.290 --> 45:02.760
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
